  2018,"10",/general-conference/2018/10/the-sustaining-of-church-officers,President Henry B. Eyring,19,"It is proposed that we release with appreciation for their devoted service Elders Mervyn B. Arnold, Craig A. Cardon, Larry J. Echo Hawk, C. Scott Grow, Allan F. Packer, Gregory A. Schwitzer, and Claudio D. Zivic as General Authority Seventies and grant them emeritus status."
  2018,"10",/general-conference/2018/10/the-sustaining-of-church-officers,President Henry B. Eyring,20,"Those who wish to join with us in expressing gratitude to these Brethren for their remarkable service, please so manifest."
  2018,"10",/general-conference/2018/10/the-sustaining-of-church-officers,President Henry B. Eyring,21,"It is proposed that we release the following as Area Seventies: B. Sergio Antunes, Alan C. Batt, R. Randall Bluth, Hans T. Boom, Fernando E. Calderón, H. Marcelo Cardus, Paul R. Coward, Marion B. De Antuñano, Robert A. Dryden, Daniel F. Dunnigan, Jeffrey D. Erekson, Mervyn C. Giddey, João Roberto Grahl, Richard K. Hansen, Todd B. Hansen, Michael R. Jensen, Daniel W. Jones, Steven O. Laing, Axel H. Leimer, Tasara Makasi, Alvin F. Meredith III, Adonay S. Obando, Katsuyuki Otahara, Fred A. Parker, José C. Pineda, Gary S. Price, Miguel A. Reyes, Alfredo L. Salas, Netzahualcoyotl Salinas, Michael L. Southward, G. Lawrence Spackman, William H. Stoddard, Stephen E. Thompson, David J. Thomson, George J. Tobias, Jacques A. Van Reenen, Raul Edgardo A. Vicencio, Keith P. Walker, and Daniel Yirenya-Tawiah."
  2018,"10",/general-conference/2018/10/the-sustaining-of-church-officers,President Henry B. Eyring,22,"Those who wish to join us in expressing appreciation for their excellent service, please manifest it."
